name: THE TICKLE - Issue #26
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

Issue #26 features artists André da Costa (@dacosta_works), V5MT (@v5mt_tv), collector/curator Sutan (@Creepyto), and a short story by Amber Duivenvoorden (@duivenvoo1).

Created by artist Wily Guys (@guyswily) with help from Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush)
